		{
			description: [
				"Two months after the fall of the Queendom of Red Barar. I was lucky to escape the calamity unscathed, albeit my power still remains low and hunters roam the land. They are on my trail. I may not have much longer to write these words."
				""
				"To whoever finds this book, do know I am the last of a decimated nobility that once served the Blood Queen. Yes, a noble sanguine. By the time you have read this, we may all have fallen into the abyss of history."
			]
