		{
			dependencies: ["19AC0B8C0B44FA30"]
			description: [
				"Anyone of any Path can create man-made paths, such as path blocks made through a shovel interaction with dirt, wood, stone, bricks, etc."
				""
				"&mYou have to place a sign anywhere within a man-made path and place a second one anywhere else. To link the two, you have to sneak punch the first and then sneak punch the second sign. Then, whenever you punch the sign, you will fast travel to the other end.&r"
			]
			icon: "via_romana:charting_map"
