		{
			dependencies: ["19AC0B8C0B44FA30"]
			description: [
				"How painful! The rays of the sun weaken me significantly. My power has waned considerably, thus the sun does not turn me to ash. I am still very much uncomfortable during the day and this will only grow."
				""
				"A hat is not enough to shield my body from the light. An umbrella is elegant enough while being as large as me. I should have escaped with my grandfather's relic umbrella. It was infinitely durable and even more stylish. Alas, I must make my own umbrella with a puny iron, gold, or diamond rod."
			]
